{"id":159779,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2011/06/我爱未未-6月7日，美国马萨诸塞州雕塑公园decordova-加入/","date":"2011-06-10T05:30:39Z","modified":"2011-06-10T05:30:39Z","title":"我爱未未 | 6月7日，美国马萨诸塞州雕塑公园deCordova 加入国际声援艾未未的行列，悬挂条幅要求释放艾未未","content":"<p><div></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span><img src=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-WTJZkO2RT6c/TfFt96imVfI/AAAAAAAAAPM/36_IHIWQHXw/s400/AiWeiWeibanner2.JPG\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" /></span></div>\n<div><span><span title=\"Click for alternate translations\">位于</span></span><span>美国马萨诸塞州林肯镇的</span><span><span title=\"Click for alternate translations\">deCordova</span><span title=\"Click for alternate translations\">雕塑公园</span><span title=\"Click for alternate translations\">博物馆，将</span><span title=\"Click for alternate translations\">一个写着“释放艾未未”的红色条</span><span title=\"Click for alternate translations\">幅</span><span title=\"Click for alternate translations\">悬挂</span><span title=\"Click for alternate translations\">在其外墙上，以此“</span><span title=\"Click for alternate translations\">回应中国最近逮捕和扣押</span><span title=\"Click for alternate translations\">著名的</span><span title=\"Click for alternate translations\">中国</span><span title=\"Click for alternate translations\">艺术家艾未未”</span><span title=\"Click for alternate translations\">。</span><span title=\"Click for alternate translations\">此外，它还在前台</span><span title=\"Click for alternate translations\">提给给参观者提供相关传单，以</span><span title=\"Click for alternate translations\">提高他们对</span></span><span>国际</span><span><span title=\"Click for alternate translations\">不公正</span><span title=\"Click for alternate translations\">的认识</span><span title=\"Click for alternate translations\">。<a rel=\"nofollow\" name=\"more\"></a></span></span></div>\n<div><span><span title=\"Click for alternate translations\"><br /></span></span></div>\n<div><span title=\"Click for alternate translations\"><span>The deCordova Sculpture Park and Museum in Lincoln, Massachusetts,hoisted a red banner saying &#8220;Free Ai Weiwei&#8221; on its facade &#8220;in response to the recent arrest and detainment of celebrated Chinese Artist Ai Weiwei&#8221;. Additionally it is providing &#8220;informational handouts at the front desk to educate visitors and raise awareness of this international injustice.&#8221;</span></span></div>\n<div><span title=\"Click for alternate translations\"><span><br /></span></span></div>\n<div><span title=\"Click for alternate translations\"><span>@deCordovaSPandM:deCordovaSPandM deCordova is joining the international support and call for release of celebrated artist Ai Weiwei http://twitpic.com/57wse7 </span></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<p>报道链接：2011年6月8日 http://goo.gl/ssOZ1</p>\n<div></div>\n<div><img width=\"1\" height=\"1\" src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/tracker/4214948278400391962-9168401214485506230?l=loveaiww.blogspot.com\" alt=\"\" /></div>\n<p><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/loveAiWeiwei/~4/soZgNRcojvw\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" /></p>\n<p><small>本文由自动聚合程序取自网络，内容和观点不代表数字时代立场</small></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://www.feedblitz.com/f/f.fbz?AddNewUserDirect\">\n定期获得翻墙信息？<a href=\"http://www.feedblitz.com/f/?Sub=750556\">请电邮订阅数字时代</a> <br /><input name=\"EMAIL\" maxlength=\"64\" type=\"text\" size=\"25\" value=\"\"><br />\n<input name=\"FEEDID\" type=\"hidden\" value=\"750556\"><br />\n<input name=\"PUBLISHER\" type=\"hidden\" value=\"7485568\"><br />\n<input type=\"submit\" value=\"订阅!\"><br />\n</form>\n","author":671,"categories":[1],"tags":[9484]}